# n8n Workflow

- Node name: unique, dễ đọc. Connections dùng `name` không phải `id`
- Position: cách nhau ~200px
- Code node: return array of `{ json, binary? }`
- Expression: `{{ $json.fieldName }}`, `{{ $input.all() }}`

Workflows cần: Schedule → POST /ingest/fetch | Webhook draft → notify | Approve → POST /publish
